    <h2>How to Ask for Google Reviews by Occasion</h2>
    <p>The biggest mistake businesses make when asking for reviews is using the same generic template for every customer. A first-time visitor needs a different approach than a loyal regular. A customer whose complaint you just resolved needs careful, appreciative language. This tool recognizes five distinct occasions and generates appropriate templates for each.</p>

